{"tid":1375210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快趣換衫方法","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:05:57.000Z","uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8bc3f75977262874f14d6ec4123e29e87caf13","tid":1375210,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"黑衫又好，白衫又衫，灰衫又衫<br />\n發覺冇乜人講<br />\n-<br />\n帶多件外套恤衫，薄薄地，咩色都好<br />\n即刻着上身，慳返換衫嘅時間<br />\n啱晒絲打們，遮住身材，費事俾啲色狼睇蝕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-<br />\n巴打又可以唔使當街剝衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n-<br />\n我底衫著黑色唔得嘅咩"},{"pid":"71bd90a68b29479188620d179e8f7651911a8288","tid":1375210,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=76f85250\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"}]}